| EA12 | LU  |  1999   |  2500    |     
| EA12 | NL  |  1999   |  2500    |     
| EA12 | PT  |  1999   |  2500    |     
| EA12 | EL  |  2001   |  2500    |     
while:

~~~sas
	%zone_to_ctry(EU28, ctrydsn=dsn);
~~~
will return (note the absence of `time`) in the dataset `dsn` the following table:
| zone | geo | 
|------|-----|
| EU28 |  AT |
| EU28 |  BE | 
| EU28 |  BG |
| EU28 |  CY |
| EU28 |  CZ |
